  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your connection to the ocean runs within your very blood, as you feel a primal draw to any bodies of water, or that contain water Starting at 11th level, you can spend 1 Minute concentrating. You know the location of any liquid within 30ft of you, and what kind liquid it is. (Water, Alcohol, Poison Etc. Not exactly brands or brews). Additionally, at the start of a rest, select any Jutsu with the Water Release Keyword that you qualify for. That justu is added to your Jutsu List until your next rest. One per rest, you may cast it without paying Charka (For Jutsu with the <em>Special</em> Cost, instead half its Chakra cost)</p><p>Starring at 18th level, you may Select a 2nd jutsu to gain the benefits of this feature, and cast each for free once per rest.</p>",
